# Routine Finder Quiz - Project Conventions

## Project Overview

This is the Dermalogica Routine Finder Quiz - a quiz application that helps users discover their ideal skincare routine.

## General Guidelines

- Write clear, maintainable code with descriptive names
- Prefer composition over inheritance
- Keep components and functions focused and single-purpose
- Add comments for non-obvious logic; let code be self-documenting where possible

## Code Style

- Use consistent formatting (run formatter/linter before committing)
- Prefer `const` over `let`; avoid `var`
- Use meaningful variable and function names that reflect their purpose

## Error Handling

- Handle errors gracefully with user-friendly messages
- Log errors for debugging; avoid silent failures
- Validate user input before processing
